gobblin.data.management.copy.replication

Class ReplicationConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.copy.replication.ReplicationConfiguration

  • public class ReplicationConfiguration
extends Object
    Class ReplicationConfiguration is used to describe the overall configuration of the replication flow for a dataset, including:
    • Replication copy mode ReplicationCopyMode
    • Meta data ReplicationMetaData
    • Replication source EndPoint
    • Replication replicas EndPoint
    • Replication topology DataFlowTopology
